<emphasis id="2ACAEA8BFFE2FFE1913ED5792D2F5212" box="[800,890,1347,1372]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="271">Mycetia</emphasis>
sp.
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="DFBE4D1AFFE2FFE191ACD5782A7F5213" box="[946,1066,1346,1373]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="3" pageNumber="271" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Rubiaceae</taxonomicName>
) and 
<taxonomicName id="DFBE4D1AFFE2FFE19674D5782BF95212" authority="Griff." authorityName="Griff." box="[1130,1452,1346,1372]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Wallichia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="3" pageNumber="271" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolia">
<emphasis id="2ACAEA8BFFE2FFE19674D5782B305212" box="[1130,1381,1346,1372]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="271">Wallichia oblongifolia</emphasis>
Griff.
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="DFBE4D1AFFE2FFE1928ED55C2F5952CE" box="[144,268,1382,1408]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="3" pageNumber="271" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Arecaceae</taxonomicName>
). Given the single location and lack of protection for the area, we assessed 
<taxonomicName id="DFBE4D1AFFE2FFE19656D55D2B6852CE" authorityName="Taram, D. Borah &amp; M. Hughes. A, Habit" authorityYear="2021" box="[1096,1341,1382,1408]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Begoniaceae" genus="Begonia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Cucurbitales" pageId="3" pageNumber="271" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="kekarmonyingensis">
<emphasis id="2ACAEA8BFFE2FFE19656D55D2B6852CE" box="[1096,1341,1382,1408]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="271">B. kekarmonyingensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to belong to the Vulnerable IUCN category under criteria VU D1 &amp; D2 (IUCN Standards and Petitions Subcommittee, 2017).
</paragraph>
